('7988','120','1','7','sacral-neuromodulation-seen-to-ease-ms-related-bladder-dysfunction-multiple-sclerosis-news-today.html','Sacral neuromodulation seen to ease MS-related bladder dysfunction - Multiple Sclerosis News Today','https://multiplesclerosisnewstoday.com/news-posts/2025/03/21/sacral-neuromodulation-eases-ms-related-bladder-dysfunction/','Steve Bryson, PhD','1 minute',NULL,'Sacral neuromodulation (SNM), in which an implanted device delivers mild electrical pulses to the nerves that control the bladder, led to sustained improvements in urinary function in half of people … [+5183 chars]','Sacral neuromodulation seen to ease MS-related bladder dysfunction - Multiple Sclerosis News Today','Steve Bryson, PhD,health,ibspotlight','Sacral neuromodulation, in which electrical pulses from an implanted device help control the bladder, was found to ease symptoms in MS.','1','1','1',NULL,'1','https://multiplesclerosisnewstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GIPain-1.png','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','1'),
('7989','120','1','7','parents-of-texas-child-who-died-of-measles-say-not-to-get-vaccine-chron.html','Parents of Texas child who died of measles say not to get vaccine - Chron','https://www.chron.com/news/article/texas-measles-couple-child-vaccine-20234021.php','Brammhi Balarajan','1 minute','','Measles cases top 300 in Texas.\r\nBSIP/Universal Images Group via Getty\r\nA Texas couple whose child died last month after contracting measles said they would not recommend the vaccine. \r\nIn an intervi… [+2636 chars]','Parents of Texas child who died of measles say not to get vaccine - Chron','Brammhi Balarajan,health,ibspotlight','A Texas couple whose child died after contracting measles says not to get the vaccine.','1','1','1',NULL,'1','https://s.hdnux.com/photos/01/47/61/41/27203709/7/rawImage.jpg','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-04-02 21:13:25','0'),
