('7991','120','1','7','doctors-warn-about-increasing-sloth-fever-infections-in-the-ushow-to-stay-safe-best-life.html','Doctors Warn About Increasing \"Sloth Fever\" Infections in the U.S.—How to Stay Safe - Best Life','https://bestlifeonline.com/sloth-fever-march-2025/','Dana Schulz','1 minute',NULL,'No, you don\'t get \"sloth fever\" from sloths, but you do get it from biting midges (also called \"no-see-ums\") and certain mosquitoes. Oropouche virus, as it\'s formally known, isn\'t a new problem (it\'s… [+5240 chars]','Doctors Warn About Increasing \"Sloth Fever\" Infections in the U.S.—How to Stay Safe - Best Life','Dana Schulz,health,ibspotlight','The busy spring break travel season could be especially risky for pregnant women.','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://bestlifeonline.com/media-library/image.jpg?id=58387487&width=1200&height=600&coordinates=0%2C100%2C0%2C100','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7992','120','1','7','tattoos-could-be-a-hidden-cancer-risk-study-of-twins-finds-gizmodo.html','Tattoos Could Be a Hidden Cancer Risk, Study of Twins Finds - Gizmodo','https://gizmodo.com/tattoos-could-be-a-hidden-cancer-risk-study-of-twins-finds-2000578684','Ed Cara','1 minute',NULL,'Your next tattoo might be riskier than currently assumed, recent research suggests. Scientists found evidence of a potential link between tattoo ink and a higher risk of certain cancers.\r\nResearchers… [+4011 chars]','Tattoos Could Be a Hidden Cancer Risk, Study of Twins Finds - Gizmodo','Ed Cara,health,ibspotlight','Twins who got tattoos had a higher risk of being diagnosed with skin cancer and lymphoma.','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/03/Tattoo-1.jpg','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7993','120','1','7','crucial-mrna-vaccine-research-at-risk-in-the-us-dw-english.html','Crucial mRNA vaccine research at risk in the US - DW (English)','https://www.dw.com/en/crucial-mrna-vaccine-research-at-risk-in-the-us/a-71989604','Carla Bleiker','1 minute',NULL,'The United States has undergone several changes in foreign and domestic policy since US President Donald Trump took office in January. Scientists who rely on federal grants for their work have been p… [+5387 chars]','Crucial mRNA vaccine research at risk in the US - DW (English)','Carla Bleiker,health,ibspotlight','Scientists in the US who do research on mRNA technology worry their funding may be cut under President Trump. mRNA technology is the basis for COVID- and other vaccines and could play a role in cancer treatment.','0','1','1','2025-04-10 06:11:50','1','https://static.dw.com/image/70038971_6.jpg','0','1',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7994','120','1','7','how-the-language-of-job-postings-can-attract-rule-bending-narcissists-ars-technica.html','How the language of job postings can attract rule-bending narcissists - Ars Technica','https://arstechnica.com/science/2025/03/how-the-language-of-job-postings-can-attract-rule-bending-narcissists/','The Conversation','1 minute',NULL,'','How the language of job postings can attract rule-bending narcissists - Ars Technica','The Conversation,health,ibspotlight','Looking to hire someone? Check your wording very carefully.','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/helpwanted-1152x648.jpg','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7995','120','1','7','new-two-measles-exposures-reported-traveling-through-dca-last-friday-arlnow.html','NEW: Two measles exposures reported traveling through DCA last Friday - ARLnow','https://www.arlnow.com/2025/03/21/new-two-measles-cases-reported-traveling-through-arlington-last-friday/','Dan Egitto','1 minute',NULL,'Two measles exposures were reported at Reagan National Airport and on the Yellow Line last Friday.\r\nExposures were possible on the airport’s terminal shuttle bus between noon and 2:30 p.m., the Virgi… [+7362 chars]','NEW: Two measles exposures reported traveling through DCA last Friday - ARLnow','Dan Egitto,health,ibspotlight','Two measles exposures were reported at Reagan National Airport and on the Yellow Line last Friday. Exposures were possible on the airport\'s terminal shuttle bus between noon and 2:30 p.m., the Virginia Department of Health announced in a press release yesterd…','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://www.arlnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Screen-Shot-2021-02-23-at-12.20.00-PM-e1614103151321.jpg','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7996','120','1','7','dont-get-surgery-on-a-friday-voxcom.html','Don’t get surgery on a Friday - Vox.com','https://www.vox.com/health/405248/hospital-surgery-knee-heart-what-day','Dylan Scott','1 minute',NULL,'If you have any say, you might want to avoid scheduling your next surgery on a Friday.\r\nThe most comprehensive analysis of what happens to patients who have surgery on Fridays versus Mondays, publish… [+3365 chars]','Don’t get surgery on a Friday - Vox.com','Dylan Scott,health,ibspotlight','The best day to get health care at the hospital is probably Monday, when more experienced doctors and nurses are on call.','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://platform.vox.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/GettyImages-1050175056.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C14.202123920531%2C100%2C71.595752158937&w=1200','0','1',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
('7997','120','1','7','the-1-surprising-exercise-for-reducing-visceral-fat-according-to-experts-eatingwell.html','The #1 Surprising Exercise for Reducing Visceral Fat, According to Experts - EatingWell','https://www.eatingwell.com/best-surprising-exercise-reducing-visceral-fat-11700565','https://www.facebook.com/EatingWell/','1 minute',NULL,'<ul><li>Excess visceral fat can increase your risk for chronic diseases like heart disease and diabetes.  </li><li>Lifting weights is one of the most effective ways to help reduce visceral fat. </li>… [+6452 chars]','The #1 Surprising Exercise for Reducing Visceral Fat, According to Experts - EatingWell','https://www.facebook.com/EatingWell/,health,ibspotlight','Find out why weight lifting is the best exercise for reducing visceral fat, according to experts. It’s simple, customizable and can be done at home.','1','1','0',NULL,'1','https://www.eatingwell.com/thmb/6A4iuZQhuLBkzwgerpGGs1wIS34=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Visceral-Fat-Lifting-Weights-mar-2025-2bbdcd2dcb114b69a367babf3c72eace.jpg','0','0',NULL,NULL,'0','0','0','2025-03-23 04:32:07','2025-03-23 04:32:07','0'),
